overview: February 21st, 2009 :: In a King of Trios qualifier, The Roughnecks battle The Order Of The Neo Solar Temple and Sami Callihan! The Colony wants revenge against F.I.S.T. for their actions against Worker Ant! Equinox makes his first Young Lions Cup defense at this event. Matches featured:  1. Eddie Kingston, Brodie Lee & Grizzly Redwood vs Sami Callihan & The Order Of The Neo Solar Temple  2. Ophidian vs Frightmare  3. Daizee Haze & Hailey Hatred vs Sara Del Rey & Sassy Stephie  4. Escorpion Egipcio vs Lince Dorado  5. F.I.S.T. vs The Colony  6. The UnStable vs Create-A-Wrestler & Sea Donsters  7. Gran Akuma vs Claudio Castagnoli  8. Cheech & Cloudy vs Jigsaw & Mike Quackenbush  9. Young Lions Cup Match Amasis vs Equinox
title: Chikara Motive, Means, Opportunity
